{"tid":1917064,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［回帶］2018年一名警員撞斃殉職 警方封閉東九龍走廊俾親友路祭","createTime":"2020-03-09T09:13:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-09T11:24:10.000Z","uid":22556,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1a681b01dd3acf05b24d292b319195cdb52b7490","tid":1917064,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T09:13:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9o8EfZC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9o8EfZC.jpg&h=50108fc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方西九龍交通部高級警員林海雲，昨晨執勤期間被駛至密斗貨車撞斃殉職，警方將於下午2時半，安排其親人重返現場東九龍走廊向尖沙嘴方向近和衷街進行路祭，預計半小時完成。<br />\n<br />\n屆時警方會實施封路措施：東廊向尖沙嘴全線封閉，1線只供警方安排的車輛作行駛用，2線用膠筒圍封分别作為拜祭區(近和衷街)， 及泊車區(近東廊天橋斜路頂)。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180323/57984818\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180323%2F57984818&d=80SwoNSEtZKcYq6iNhm%2FM4tKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=49ce8736\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180323%2F57984818&h=ce3a3f00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180323/57984818</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1474101479504603/posts/2546902138891193/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1474101479504603%2Fposts%2F2546902138891193%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=80SwoNSEtZKcYq6iNhm%2FM4tKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=a8c4ca04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1474101479504603/posts/2546902138891193/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"237293b4391226b5e37118db3cc2e18a0c87e192","tid":1917064,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T09:15:29.000Z","msg":"特權貴族<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f672b74803883cd00f8b168c4e924c6283dd576","tid":1917064,"uid"